    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "CANADA\nVANCOUVER\nU. S. A.\nTo London\nNew York\nCALL YOUR LOCAL\nTRAVEL AGENT\nOR\nSAN FRANCISCO\nBrilish\nCommonwealth Pacific\nAirlines\nLIMITED\nHead Office: A.P.A. Building, 53 Martin Place\nSydney.\nTelephone: BIV 2741\nHONOLULU\n)CANTON 1.\nNeen\nThe NORTH AMERICAN ROUTE Between\nENGLAND \u0026 AUSTRALIA or NEW ZEALAND\nEarly bookings are available on the through route\nvia the U.S.A. or Canada! The London-New York\nroute connects with B.C.P.A. at San Francisco, the\nLondon-Montreal route at Vancouver.\nNo hotel\nexpenses on through bookings when all connections\nmade ... where desired, stop-overs arranged at\nno extra fare. Full fare payable in sterling, Aust-\nralian or New Zealand currency.\nInternational\nDate\nAUSTRALIA\nSYDNEY\nAUCKLAND",
